text: He Can Do the Impossible, released in 1994 on CGI Records, is a gospel music album by American contemporary gospel music group Witness. The album reached No. 12 on the Billboard Gospel Albums chart. ==Track listing== #"He Can Do the Impossible" #"We Give Thanks" #"Just as You Are" #"More Than the World Against You" #"Where Would I Be" #"When I Pray" #"You'll Never Walk Alone" #"It's Your Time" #"After the Storm Is Gone" #"It's Raining in My Life Again" ==Personnel== *Lisa Page Brooks: Vocals *Laeh Page: Vocals *Diane Campbell: Vocals *Lou Ann Stewart: Vocals ==Charts== {| class="wikitable" !
